<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="202" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="5.[813,1451,297,559]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[813,948,297,321]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Diagnosis. –</emphasis>
Similar to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Simon" baseAuthorityYear="1888" box="[1063,1240,297,320]" class="Arachnida" family="Barychelidae" genus="Sason" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="andamanicum">
<emphasis box="[1063,1240,297,320]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">S. andamanicum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, male distinguished by: cuspules on labium and maxillae quite short and stout (
<figureCitation box="[821,970,365,388]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="7.[113,158,2008,2029]" captionTargetBox="[125,1431,308,1898]" captionTargetId="figure-84@7.[121,1448,294,1912]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figs. 33-41. Sason hirsutum, new species, male holotype. 33, body (without legs and palps), dorsal view; 34, eye group, dorsal view; 35, labium and proximal portion of maxillae, ventral view; 36, maxillae, labium and sternum, ventral view; 37, opisthosoma, ventral view; 38, left tibia I, prolateral view; 39, the same, ventral view; 40, distal part of palpus, ventral view; 41, the same, retrolateral view. Scale lines (33+37; 34; 35; 36; 38-41) = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619387" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4619387/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Figs. 35, 36</figureCitation>
); tibia I with row of longer and thinner retroventral spines; tibial spur less elevated, situated more distally, carrying a megaspine less strongly inclined from axis of leg (
<figureCitation box="[952,1037,467,490]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="7.[113,158,2008,2029]" captionTargetBox="[125,1431,308,1898]" captionTargetId="figure-84@7.[121,1448,294,1912]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figs. 33-41. Sason hirsutum, new species, male holotype. 33, body (without legs and palps), dorsal view; 34, eye group, dorsal view; 35, labium and proximal portion of maxillae, ventral view; 36, maxillae, labium and sternum, ventral view; 37, opisthosoma, ventral view; 38, left tibia I, prolateral view; 39, the same, ventral view; 40, distal part of palpus, ventral view; 41, the same, retrolateral view. Scale lines (33+37; 34; 35; 36; 38-41) = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619387" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4619387/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Fig. 39</figureCitation>
); distal margin of tibia I less deeply invaginated (
<figureCitation box="[952,1030,502,525]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="7.[113,158,2008,2029]" captionTargetBox="[125,1431,308,1898]" captionTargetId="figure-84@7.[121,1448,294,1912]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figs. 33-41. Sason hirsutum, new species, male holotype. 33, body (without legs and palps), dorsal view; 34, eye group, dorsal view; 35, labium and proximal portion of maxillae, ventral view; 36, maxillae, labium and sternum, ventral view; 37, opisthosoma, ventral view; 38, left tibia I, prolateral view; 39, the same, ventral view; 40, distal part of palpus, ventral view; 41, the same, retrolateral view. Scale lines (33+37; 34; 35; 36; 38-41) = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619387" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4619387/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Fig. 38</figureCitation>
); bulb with basally thinner, not sigmoid embolus (
<figureCitation box="[920,1055,536,559]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="7.[113,158,2008,2029]" captionTargetBox="[125,1431,308,1898]" captionTargetId="figure-84@7.[121,1448,294,1912]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figs. 33-41. Sason hirsutum, new species, male holotype. 33, body (without legs and palps), dorsal view; 34, eye group, dorsal view; 35, labium and proximal portion of maxillae, ventral view; 36, maxillae, labium and sternum, ventral view; 37, opisthosoma, ventral view; 38, left tibia I, prolateral view; 39, the same, ventral view; 40, distal part of palpus, ventral view; 41, the same, retrolateral view. Scale lines (33+37; 34; 35; 36; 38-41) = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619387" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4619387/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Figs. 40, 41</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="8" lastPageNumber="205" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="5.[813,1452,604,900]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[813,968,604,628]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Description. –</emphasis>
<collectingRegion box="[976,1031,604,627]" country="Maldives" name="Maale" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Male</collectingRegion>
(
<typeStatus box="[1046,1147,604,627]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">holotype</typeStatus>
). Coloration uniformly light reddish brown on dorsal side, ventral side lighter. Opisthosoma cream, with dark brown-violet pattern dorsally (
<figureCitation box="[821,898,706,729]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="7.[113,158,2008,2029]" captionTargetBox="[125,1431,308,1898]" captionTargetId="figure-84@7.[121,1448,294,1912]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figs. 33-41. Sason hirsutum, new species, male holotype. 33, body (without legs and palps), dorsal view; 34, eye group, dorsal view; 35, labium and proximal portion of maxillae, ventral view; 36, maxillae, labium and sternum, ventral view; 37, opisthosoma, ventral view; 38, left tibia I, prolateral view; 39, the same, ventral view; 40, distal part of palpus, ventral view; 41, the same, retrolateral view. Scale lines (33+37; 34; 35; 36; 38-41) = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619387" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4619387/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Fig. 33</figureCitation>
) and ventrally (
<figureCitation box="[1067,1146,706,729]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="7.[113,158,2008,2029]" captionTargetBox="[125,1431,308,1898]" captionTargetId="figure-84@7.[121,1448,294,1912]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figs. 33-41. Sason hirsutum, new species, male holotype. 33, body (without legs and palps), dorsal view; 34, eye group, dorsal view; 35, labium and proximal portion of maxillae, ventral view; 36, maxillae, labium and sternum, ventral view; 37, opisthosoma, ventral view; 38, left tibia I, prolateral view; 39, the same, ventral view; 40, distal part of palpus, ventral view; 41, the same, retrolateral view. Scale lines (33+37; 34; 35; 36; 38-41) = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619387" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4619387/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Fig. 37</figureCitation>
). Ocular area dark; posterior zone in front of eyes grey, anterior zone hyaline with black median patch (
<figureCitation box="[970,1050,775,798]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="7.[113,158,2008,2029]" captionTargetBox="[125,1431,308,1898]" captionTargetId="figure-84@7.[121,1448,294,1912]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figs. 33-41. Sason hirsutum, new species, male holotype. 33, body (without legs and palps), dorsal view; 34, eye group, dorsal view; 35, labium and proximal portion of maxillae, ventral view; 36, maxillae, labium and sternum, ventral view; 37, opisthosoma, ventral view; 38, left tibia I, prolateral view; 39, the same, ventral view; 40, distal part of palpus, ventral view; 41, the same, retrolateral view. Scale lines (33+37; 34; 35; 36; 38-41) = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619387" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4619387/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Fig. 34</figureCitation>
). Leg tarsi and distal part of metatarsi ventrally white; distal portion of tibia IV and lateral sides of patella IV slightly darkened. Dorsodistal portion of cymbium white.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619385" ID-Zenodo-Dep="4619385" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4619385/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" startId="5.[117,162,2035,2056]" targetBox="[127,1450,965,1963]" targetPageId="5">
